{"tid":785391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高中生女兒走路怪怪的　母揭她一夜戰二次","createTime":"2018-08-19T07:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T07:41:16.000Z","uid":29627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ca6a0eb31c845a7a82ffc32825825d7bb36ad7","tid":785391,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"是女兒走路太奇怪，還是媽媽太厲害&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n《聯合報》報導，桃園市潘姓男子（23歲）1年多前在網路上認識讀高中的少女，他約女生到住處，女生對家人說「要到同學家溫習功課」，卻到潘男家發生親密關係，一晚二度親熱。隔天清晨返家時，女高中生走路姿勢怪怪的，被母親發現好像有點跛，女兒承認前晚和潘男發生性關係時太激烈，早上覺得有點痛，走路才不順，女生母親氣得控告潘男妨害性自主。<br />\n <br />\n桃園地院審理時，潘姓男子坦承和女生發生2次性關係，都是經過女生同意。女生說和潘是男女朋友「有點喜歡他」，由於女生未滿16歲，潘仍構成妨害性自主罪，法官依2個妨害性自主罪判他5個月徒刑、沒有宣告緩刑，一旦確定，還是要坐牢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180819/1413686/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180819%2F1413686%2F&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=40cc7acb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180819%2F1413686%2F&h=bf8017d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180819/1413686/</a>"},{"pid":"1773e515166511394c38d1b50c0b6ebd30e20608","tid":785391,"uid":17081,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/1e/242205_499898256696035_1994565062_o.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130211081442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F1e%2F242205_499898256696035_1994565062_o.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130211081442&h=9dd60f8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"211995ca7c68d7c3f291b63bc593f47be391706b","tid":785391,"uid":52358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T07:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/154113_8ae849bccec81d007323cb4624a246e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://